{
  "title": "Credit card minimum payment trap",
  "script": "Credit Card ka minimum payment trap! Kya aap bhi har mahine sirf minimum amount pay karte ho? Toh suno, yeh aapko debt ke daldal mein phansa sakta hai! Maan lo, aapka bill hai 30,000 rupaye aur minimum payment hai sirf 1,500 rupaye. Lekin baaki 28,500 rupaye par high interest lagna shuru ho jaata hai. Toh debt kam hone ke bajaye, sirf interest badhta jaayega. Hamesha full outstanding amount pay karein. Minimum payment is a trap, not a solution! Finplaza ko follow karein!",
